      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been curated for the discerning motorist who prioritizes both performance and presentation. Meticulously maintained and showing pride of ownership, it offers a refined cabin environment and mechanical consistency that ensures a superior driving experience. This acquisition represents a balanced investment in quality and longevity, standing as a testament to diligent preservation and engineering excellence.",
